Simple Calculator Using C
Project Overview

Simple Calculator is a menu-driven application developed in C language to perform basic arithmetic operations. The program allows users to enter numbers and select an operation to calculate the result.

This project was created to practice fundamental programming concepts such as switch case, loops, user input, and arithmetic operations.

Features
Addition
Subtraction
Multiplication
Division
Menu Driven Interface
Exit Option
Concepts Used
C Programming
Switch Case
Loops (do-while)
Variables and Data Types
Arithmetic Operators
User Input Handling
